== Installation and Quick Start

=== System Requirements

==== Hardware Requirements

* NVIDIA GPU with CUDA support (recommended for best performance)
* 8GB+ RAM
* 10GB+ free disk space

==== Software Requirements

* NVIDIA Omniverse USD Composer (or Create)
* Python 3.10 or higher
* NVIDIA Warp (for GPU acceleration)
* Windows 10/11, Linux, or macOS

=== Installation Steps

==== Step 1: Copy Extension Folder

----
Source: exts/qixotic.tendroids/
Destination: <omniverse-app>/exts/qixotic.tendroids/
----

==== Step 2: Enable Extension

1. Open NVIDIA Omniverse USD Composer
2. Navigate to: Window → Extensions
3. Search for "Tendroids"
4. Toggle extension to enabled state

==== Step 3: Verify Installation

* Check for "Tendroid Controls" in Window menu
* Console should display: `[TendroidsExtension] Starting up`
* Control panel window should be available

=== Quick Start Guide

==== Basic Workflow

[cols="1,3"]
|===
|Step |Action

|1
|Open Control Panel: Window → Tendroid Controls

|2
|Configure Parameters: Adjust diameter, length, wave settings

|3
|Spawn Creatures: Click "Spawn Tendroids" button

|4
|Start Animation: Click "Start Animation" button

|5
|Observe: Watch smooth breathing wave travel up creatures
