==== First-Time Experience

For your first test run:

1. Leave all default values unchanged
2. Click "Spawn Tendroids" (creates 1 Tendroid)
3. Click "Start Animation"
4. Observe smooth breathing wave traveling upward

You should see a cylindrical creature with a flared base performing organic breathing animation.

